  <summary>Personal media library and downloader</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>MIT</project_license>
  <developer_name>calvarr</developer_name>
  <description>
    <p>
      DLPulse Next is a cross-platform desktop app for educational use and personal
      media libraries. It wraps yt-dlp and ffmpeg to resolve supported public URLs,
      manage a local archive, play media, and cast to Chromecast devices.
    </p>
    <p>
      The native window uses GTK and WebKit2GTK. You are solely responsible for
      complying with copyright laws and each platform&apos;s terms of service.
    </p>
  </description>
